content.rendered:
On the 29th of May, Prestige Motorcars held a fun-filled morning cruise from Bengawan Solo PIK to Papparich Froggy Castle in BSD for some breakfast.

What started out as a small event for the customers of Prestige Motorcars quickly turned into a full blown event with over 30 cars participating. We set off from PIK at 8am, with the thunderous sounds of the cars and adrenaline running high the cars reached BSD in no time.

Friends from many different car clubs joined us in this morning run, including members of Lamborghini Club Indonesia, GTR Owners Club, M Owners Club Indonesia as well as Porsche Club Indonesia. All in all, it was a great morning meeting with members of different car clubs and to come together as a community of car enthusiasts.
